# Voicebox README demo GIF
# Regenerate from repo root: vhs assets/demo.tape
# Requires: https://github.com/charmbracelet/vhs

Output assets/demo.gif

Set FontSize 15
Set Width 980
Set Height 480
Set Theme "Catppuccin Mocha"
Set TypingSpeed 1ms
Set Framerate 20
Set PlaybackSpeed 1.0
Set Shell bash

Hide
Type "bash ./assets/demo.sh"
Enter
Sleep 400ms
Show
Sleep 14s
